sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as OPC UA client
    participant Endpoint as opcuapp Endpoint
    participant Dispatcher as OpcUaBinaryServiceDispatcher
    participant BinRt as OpcUaBinaryRuntime
    participant Runtime as opcua::OpcUaRuntime
    participant Conv as opcua_conversion
    participant Svc as SCADA service

    Client->>Endpoint: UA Binary request
    Endpoint->>Dispatcher: decoded service payload
    Note right of Dispatcher: Transport decode / adapter normalization happens at the Binary edge.
    Dispatcher->>BinRt: invoke decoded request
    Note right of BinRt: Binary-only runtime work is limited to token lookup and authenticated dispatch over canonical opcua:: request/response types.
    BinRt->>Runtime: canonical request dispatch
    Runtime->>Conv: convert request payload
    Conv-->>Runtime: SCADA-native inputs
    Note right of Runtime: Shared service dispatch lives in opcua::OpcUaRuntime and routes canonical requests into shared SCADA services.
    Runtime->>Svc: Read / Write / Browse / Call / AddNodes / DeleteNodes
    Svc-->>Runtime: status + results
    Runtime->>Conv: convert results
    Conv-->>Runtime: OPC UA response payload
    Runtime-->>BinRt: canonical response
    BinRt-->>Dispatcher: Binary response body
    Note right of Dispatcher: Response encoding / transport-specific exceptions stay wire-only, including HistoryReadEvents encoding.
    Dispatcher-->>Endpoint: encoded Binary response
    Endpoint-->>Client: UA Binary response
